data.description:
Welcome to your dream retreat in the heart of Acreage, FL! This magnificent 5-bedroom, 3-bathroom home is situated on a sprawling 1.32-acre lot, offering the perfect blend of space, luxury, and tranquility.As you step through the front door, you'll be greeted by an abundance of natural light that fills the open and spacious living areas. The focal point of the living space is the impact French patio doors that not only enhance the aesthetic appeal but also provide seamless access to the outdoors.Enjoy the Florida sunshine and beautiful evenings on your screened-in porch, providing a perfect outdoor oasis for relaxation and al fresco dining. The lush greenery surrounding the property adds to the overall sense of serenity and privacy.

This home also features a convenient two-car garage, ensuring ample space for parking and storage. What truly sets this property apart is the enchanting 1-bedroom 1-bath detached guest cottage, making it the focal point of this dreamy estate. provides a private retreat for visitors or can be utilized as a home office or studio. The possibilities are endless.

The well-appointed kitchen boasts modern appliances, granite countertops, and plenty of cabinet space, making it a chef's delight. The bedrooms are generously sized, providing comfortable living spaces for family members or guests.

With its prime location in Acreage, FL, this property offers a unique opportunity to experience the best of both worlds - a peaceful, residential setting with easy access to urban amenities and attractions.

Don't miss the chance to make this stunning property your new home. Schedule a showing today and envision the possibilities that await in this exceptional residence in Acreage, FL!
